  Locus:
    Page: 147
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Faith
---
Faith is a function of the heart. It must be enforced by reason. The two
are not antagonistic as some think. The more intense one’s faith is, the
more it whets one’s reason. When faith becomes blind it dies.
